<li>Fairfield County: 69</li>
<li>Hartford County: 11</li>
<li>Litchfield County: 5</li>
<li>MiddlesexCounty: 1</li>
<li>New Haven County: 10</li>
<li>Tolland County: 1 </li>
</ul>
<p>Aer Lingus delays flight through April 15</p>
<p>The airliner said on March 17, due to new US entry restrictions, 
flights to and from Hartford between March 17 and April 15 are canceled.
 </p>
<p>Wells Fargo Bank employee in Bloomfield test positive for COVID-19</p>
<p>State Representative Bobby Gibson posted on Facebook Wednesday that 
an employee at the bank tested positive for COVID-19. The bank has been 
closed and is being cleaned. </p>
